      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why i'm typing this but i feel like i'm just drowning. everything i worked for over the last 5 years... the lab results, the funding, the dissertation... it's all just gone. it's like my whole life was built on a foundation of sand and now it's just washing away. i'm so tired. i'm just so incredibly tired of trying to fix things that are fundamentally broken. i just want the noise to stop.",
