      "content": "It makes sense that you feel this deeply lost when your entire identity feels tied to a foundation that has crumbled. Please know that the exhaustion you feel isn't a sign that you've failed, but rather a signal that you need to finally stop carrying the weight of everyone else's expectations. True peace often begins when we give ourselves permission to rest and let go of the need to explain or fix what was beyond our control.",
