      "content": "but \"rest\" feels so impossible right now. even when i lay down, my head won't stop spinning about how much i've messed up. it's like there's no way to actually get away from it all. every time I think about starting over or trying to fix it, I just feel this massive wave of dread. it feels like the only way to actually get that quiet, that real peace you're talking about, is to just... not have to deal with any of it anymore. to just stop existing.",
